# UMKM Cepat Design AMD

## Source read
Reference: lovable.dev homepage. Use as inspiration only; do not copy brand, copy, exact layout, assets, or proprietary implementation.

## Design intent
UMKM Cepat should feel like a friendly AI builder for Indonesian small businesses: fast, optimistic, clear, lightweight, product-led.

## Visual language
- Base: warm off-white canvas, not pure white.
- Ink: near-black charcoal for high readability.
- Accent: single coral/rose gradient with subtle violet edge.
- Material: soft cards, thin neutral borders, large radius, low shadows.
- Motion feel: calm launch/product builder energy; no heavy neon cyber look.
- Layout: centered high-impact hero with interactive prompt surface, then airy product proof sections.

## Tokens
- Page bg: `#fbfaf8`
- Ink: `#171412`
- Muted ink: `rgba(23,20,18,.62)`
- Border: `rgba(23,20,18,.10)`
- Surface: `rgba(255,255,255,.72)`
- Accent coral: `#ff6b5f`
- Accent rose: `#f0437d`
- Accent violet: `#7c3aed`
- Soft amber: `#ffcf7a`
- Radius: cards `28px`, buttons/input `999px`, small chips `999px`
- Shadow: soft rose/charcoal tinted, never hard black

## Typography
- Use existing `font-sans`.
- Headlines: large, tight, confident; no generic AI-purple headline.
- Body: short, readable, max 65ch.
- Copy language: Indonesian, direct, UMKM-friendly.

## Components
### Header
- Translucent off-white glass.
- Compact logo + nav anchors.
- Pill CTA.
- No heavy dark bar.

### Hero
- Large centered headline.
- Subheadline concise.
- Prompt composer card as product metaphor.
- CTA inside/near composer.
- Decorative gradient orbs behind hero, clipped/subtle.

### Proof chips
- 3 short trust/value chips below hero.
- Use one icon family only.

### Feature section
- Bento-like cards, mixed sizes when useful.
- Cards show product benefits, not generic SaaS bullets.

### Workflow
- Three steps; visual timeline/cards.
- Emphasize no technical setup.

### Open-source/provider note
- Clear but secondary.
- Communicate flexible providers without overwhelming main audience.

### Footer
- Light, quiet, consistent with header.
- Brand, nav, social/support links.

## Anti-copy constraints
- Do not reuse Lovable headline wording.
- Do not copy exact hero composer DOM/classes.
- Do not use Lovable logo/imagery/templates.
- Preserve UMKM Cepat brand and domain `umkmcepat.com`.

## Quality bar
- Accessible contrast and focus-visible rings.
- Mobile-first; no horizontal overflow.
- `lint`, `typecheck`, `test`, `build` all pass.
